comments.message:
Before checking for ec, we should check if the id actually exists and return 404 if not. To get the returned value from d-bus, print the ec.value() when requesting a non-existent id, it might be it returns EBADR, then you can add the following as an example:

                if (ec.value() == EBADR)
                {
                    messages::resourceNotFound(..);
                    return;
                }
